name: Journey through the layers of the mind
description: Memo Akten (memo.tv), 2015. Created on 3rd July 2015, minted April 2021 for #TheFen on H=N <3. Perhaps the first video ever to be created with #deepdream. In recognising forms in these images, your mind has become entangled with the system, in a duet between an artificial and biological neural network, in a quest for projecting and making meaning.
